questions: On which date did the illness associated to the claim ID {claim_id} occur?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  ?currentIllnessDate WHERE {{ ?claim a syn:Claim;syn:id '{claim_id}'^^uuid:;syn:currentIllnessDate ?currentIllnessDate.}}
